                        },
                        "displayName": "Kouhei Sutou",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Asia/Tokyo"
                    },
                    "body": "I think that it's meaningless. This approach is for system Thrift not bundled Thrift.\r\n\r\nWe need to use bundled Thrift to use a patch step. But we sill need Boost to build Thrift with the patch.\r\n\r\nAnd there are still some {{#include <boost/...>}}s in public headers with the patch. e.g.:\r\n\r\n* https://github.com/apache/thrift/blob/master/lib/cpp/src/thrift/transport/TTransportException.h#L23\r\n* https://github.com/apache/thrift/blob/master/lib/cpp/src/thrift/processor/TMultiplexedProcessor.h#L26\r\n* https://github.com/apache/thrift/blob/master/lib/cpp/src/thrift/protocol/TProtocol.h#L95\r\n\r\nWe need more steps to complete this approach. \r\n",
